                                              rgo:text "et supradicti aep. Magunt. ac marchio Brandenburg., ad quorum instantiam papa [s.d. 7. febr. 47] certas concessiones sup. coll. ad quecumque benef. et eorum possessoribus edidit: decl. suas conc. n. extendi ad Theodericum [de Moers] olim aep. Colon. et Jacobum [de Sierck] olim aep. Trever. hactenus eorum eccll. privatos aut ad eorum provin. et dioc. donec p. papam aliter fuerit ordinatum s.d. [post 7. febr. 1447] V 365 480rs." ;
                                              rgo:volume "5" .


###  https://example.org/rg/sublemma/10501952-21
<https://example.org/rg/sublemma/10501952-21> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
